divs: Sighting DetailsYou know the first part, Now let me tell you that this object made no noise such as a jet or propeller driven plane, its flight path was from west to east, there were very few scattered clouds and the sun was setting at the time.It moved a little eradically not in a straight line,and slowly.I would guess it to be just above the clouds too.I have seen these before,I decided that I should all make these sightings known.They are real!!!Do you think mankind has evolved far enough to handle the truth? I do!!! All mankind has to do is learn to live in peace, that would be the first step to knowing more about them.OK, so much for my thoughts, I watched it slowly fade from sight to the east.
Summary: I walked out of my back door,Looked up and saw this object moving across the sky
